<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc1e3, #ff9aec);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.9);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #ff69b4;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        video {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 4px solid #ff69b4;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #fff;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Happy Birthday!</h1>
        <p>สุขสันต์วันเกิดขอให้มีสุขภาพแข็งแรงเสมอ มีความสุขในชีวิตนะ รักกันนานๆ</p>
        <video controls>
            <source src="happy_birthday.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
        <footer❤️ just for you!</footer>
    </div>
</
